<TEXT>
Schroders' new Japanese investment trust, the Schroder Japan Growth Fund,
has so far raised Pounds 88m from a placing of shares. Its initial size has
been capped at Pounds 125m, allowing a maximum of Pounds 37m to be raised
from a public offer, which opened yesterday and closes on June 30.
