FT  08 JUN 94 / Observer: They toil not
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
So, fresh from a relaxing sojourn at his Normandy holiday home, Peter Lilley
has agreed to reappear in support of Britain's Tory government in its
European election campaign.
It seems the secretary of state for social security will now show up in
Bradford, bolstering the hopeless cause of the Conservative candidate in
