<HEADLINE>
FT  08 JUN 94 / Intervention in Haiti ruled out
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By REUTER
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   BELEM, BRAZIL
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
The Organisation of American States has ruled out military intervention to
restore democracy in Haiti, but is expected to ban commercial flights and
tighten economic sanctions, officials said yesterday, Reuter reports from
Belem, Brazil.
